<plot>This puppet (stop-action) cartoon features a young Mexican troubadour, Pepito, who is serenading a senorita beneath her balcony, hoping to win her love. She is vastly unimpressed, however, so he goes to a music teacher to find out what is wrong with his technique. He returns as a musical-cross of 'Bing Crosby' (qv) and 'Frank Sinatra' (qv), and wins fair senorita.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?124111</url></doc>
